cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it introduces a sequence to sequence model with attention mechanism for speech recognition. It may also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with speech recognition. Additionally, it may be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it describes various neural network algorithms. It could also be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks for speech recognition.
